png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22c159c4c02a7d8976f4558b87a93b7c00df9c2","tid":212560,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"我控制示威者？<br />\n定係控制防暴警？"},{"pid":"7a05b618e39d0a4511b8a9b765235d66ead7c422","tid":212560,"uid":46965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"我睇咗RION"},{"pid":"2722d4e2e8fb05f2cd8f95155995e87f2131c347","tid":212560,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我控制示威者？<br />\n定係控制防暴警？</blockquote><br />\n差佬"},{"pid":"9b1b341918060b8150d875ab80bde97fed3c0b92","tid":212560,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我控制示威者？<br />\n定係控制防暴警？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Police</span><br />\n<br />\nEmploy numerous crowd-control tactics, both passive and aggressive.<br />\n<br />\nCommand Assault, Tactical, Ballistic, Arrest and Plain Clothes squads.<br />\n<br />\nCall in police trucks, water cannon, snatch squads and others.<br />\n<br />\nChoose whether to use smoke grenades, rubber and plastic bullets, tasers or even live ammunition.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Rioters<br />\n</span><br />\nInstruct Leaders, Agitators, Rioters (armed and passive) and Journalists.<br />\n<br />\nIncite rage and cause the masses to act aggressively or try to calm the situation with tactical crowd reformation and retreats.<br />\n<br />\nAttack authority with Molotov cocktails, fireworks, paper-bombs, rocks, street furniture and the power of the media.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Multiple Modes</span><br />\n<br />\nTwenty levels split over four campaigns Keratea (Greece), NoTAV (Italy), Indignados (Spain) and Arab Spring (Egypt).<br />\n<br />\nSee the story unfold from both sides - play all twenty levels as the Rioters or the Police.<br />\n<br />\nSingle player mode - play against the computer AI.<br />\n<br />\nSkirmish mode - play against a friend on the same computer.<br />\n<br />\nMultiplayer mode: play against a friend online.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Create your own Riots with the level editor</span><br />\n<br />\nAlter the look of the confrontation by importing your own background graphics.<br />\n<br />\nPosition elements, vehicles and obstacles where you want them.<br />\n<br />\nSet the time of day and the weather.<br />\n<br />\nChoose and position rioters and police starting points as well as their orders and level of aggression."},{"pid":"80fcbaa0dae97bf5acf028ca00f3f6cf41710263","tid":212560,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我控制示威者？<br />\n定係控制防暴警？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Police</span><br />\n<br />\nEmploy numerous crowd-control tactics, both passive and aggressive.<br />\n<br />\nCommand Assault, Tactical, Ballistic, Arrest and Plain Clothes squads.<br />\n<br />\nCall in police trucks, water cannon, snatch squads and others.<br />\n<br />\nChoose whether to use smoke grenades, rubber and plastic bullets, tasers or even live ammunition.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Rioters<br />\n</span><br />\nInstruct Leaders, Agitators, Rioters (armed and passive) and Journalists.<br />\n<br />\nIncite rage and cause the masses to act aggressively or try to calm the situation with tactical crowd reformation and retreats.<br />\n<br />\nAttack authority with Molotov cocktails, fireworks, paper-bombs, rocks, street furniture and the power of the media.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Multiple Modes</span><br />\n<br />\nTwenty levels split over four campaigns Keratea (Greece), NoTAV (Italy), Indignados (Spain) and Arab Spring (Egypt).<br />\n<br />\nSee the story unfold from both sides - play all twenty levels as the Rioters or the Police.<br />\n<br />\nSingle player mode - play against the computer AI.<br />\n<br />\nSkirmish mode - play against a friend on the same computer.<br />\n<br />\nMultiplayer mode: play against a friend online.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Create your own Riots with the level editor</span><br />\n<br />\nAlter the look of the confrontation by importing your own background graphics.<br />\n<br />\nPosition elements, vehicles and obstacles where you want them.<br />\n<br />\nSet the time of day and the weather.<br />\n<br />\nChoose and position rioters and police starting points as well as their orders and level of aggression.</blockquote><br />\n有得掟磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ed3fb0b7d8b73b9c2bd12aa44091eb2b89ebdb","tid":212560,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我控制示威者？<br />\n定係控制防暴警？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Police</span><br />\n<br />\nEmploy numerous crowd-control tactics, both passive and aggressive.<br />\n<br />\nCommand Assault, Tactical, Ballistic, Arrest and Plain Clothes squads.<br />\n<br />\nCall in police trucks, water cannon, snatch squads and others.<br />\n<br />\nChoose whether to use smoke grenades, rubber and plastic bullets, tasers or even live ammunition.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Rioters<br />\n</span><br />\nInstruct Leaders, Agitators, Rioters (armed and passive) and Journalists.<br />\n<br />\nIncite rage and cause the masses to act aggressively or try to calm the situation with tactical crowd reformation and retreats.<br />\n<br />\nAttack authority with Molotov cocktails, fireworks, paper-bombs, rocks, street furniture and the power of the media.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Multiple Modes</span><br />\n<br />\nTwenty levels split over four campaigns Keratea (Greece), NoTAV (Italy), Indignados (Spain) and Arab Spring (Egypt).<br />\n<br />\nSee the story unfold from both sides - play all twenty levels as the Rioters or the Police.<br />\n<br />\nSingle player mode - play against the computer AI.<br />\n<br />\nSkirmish mode - play against a friend on the same computer.<br />\n<br />\nMultiplayer mode: play against a friend online.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Create your own Riots with the level editor</span><br />\n<br />\nAlter the look of the confrontation by importing your own background graphics.<br />\n<br />\nPosition elements, vehicles and obstacles where you want them.<br />\n<br />\nSet the time of day and the weather.<br />\n<br />\nChoose and position rioters and police starting points as well as their orders and level of aggression.</blockquote><br />\n有得掟磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梗係今天我黎buff己方士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7445b76e458224d4cc4a20761fc696a848b3ce63","tid":212560,"uid":47523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果有個 中國版<br />\n<br />\n做示威者果邊 是否無得玩........因為對家直接出坦克<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國果關根本係nightmare 難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港係hell mode<img src=\"